<hr>
<!-- Information about social events using div containers and hero-units -->
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <h2>Socialise with us!</h2>

        Our ski club often holds social events in order to improve how our company is run as well as introducing members to each other.<br>
        <br>Outlined below are upcoming events:<br>
        <br>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <h4>Walk to Hilbre Island - Saturday 14th July 2013, 1.30pm, Starting at Dee Lane Slipway, West Kirby (near Morrison's car park)</h4>
        
        The walk to Hilbre Island is 2 miles each way and we will be crossing over at low tide however sensible clothing and footwear is recommended. Everybody is welcome to join us, including non-members.
      </div>

      <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <h4>Club AGM, Oval Sports Centre - Sunday 14th July 2013, at 5.00pm</h4>

        Would you like your say on how your ski club is run; do you have any suggestions or questions relating to the skiing sessions, training, teaching, holidays, racing or social events that you would like to share with us? Well this is your big chance. The Oval Ski Club's annual general meeting is taking place on the 14th July at the Oval Sports Centre Meeting room (within the sports centre) at 5pm.<br>
        <br>
        If that was not incentive enough, the club will also be providing free refreshments! (drinks and snacks). <br>
        <br>
        Remember the club is run entirely by volunteers without whom none of the above activities would take place. Further volunteers at Oval Ski Club are very much in demand, so if you can spare a few hours making drinks on a Saturday morning or would like to be Chairman (or any of the jobs in between) - feel free to express your interest and get in touch with us via the <a href="contact"> contact</a> webpage.<br> 
        <br>
        All committee posts will be up for election. If you interested in attending or would like more information please <a href="contact">contact</a> Jane by either phone or email.
      </div>

      <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <h4>Get in touch</h4>
      If you wish to attend any of the events listed above or want further information, you can <a href="contact">contact</a> our social secretary Jane Croft by phone on either 0151 608 4575 or 07963 906979. You can also get in touch with Jane via email at <a href ="mailto:jane.croft1@ntlworld.com">jane.croft1@ntlworld.com</a>
      </div>
      <!-- Button to check what event ideas are currently pending -->
      <p>
        <center><a class="btn btn-primary btn-large" href="../events" type="button">Pending Activities</a></center>
      </p>

      <hr>

      <footer>
      <!-- Links to Facebook and Twitter -->
      <center>&copy; Oval Ski Club 2013 &nbsp</center>
      <a href="http://www.facebook.com/group.php?gid=2256597544"><img src="../assets/facebooklogo.png" width="55" height="25" title="Like us on Facebook"><a href="https://twitter.com/OvalSki"><img src="../assets/twitter.png" width="55" height="25" title="Follow us on Twitter"></a></a>
      </footer>
    </div>

      <%= yield %>

